window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Even with his immense new power, James comes to realize that he is still playing into the hands of the System.</b></p> <p>If they are to free Earth and redeem the billions of dead, James and his crew will have to do more than journey into the pits of hell or slaughter countless armies of demonsâ€”they'll have to find the god-like forces orchestrating the apocalypse, break every rule, and utterly defeat them.</p> <p>This is the final installation in the Dawn of the Void trilogy. Discover the exciting end to James's desperate attempts to save humanity before the unleashing of the Void.</p>"; 
